Class EmployeeConnector.EmployeeCallback<T>

    public static class EmployeeConnector.EmployeeCallback<T>

implements ServiceConnector.Callback<T>
    An implementation of the ServiceConnector.Callback interface for receiving asynchronous results from EmployeeConnector methods that provides default method implementations.

    The default implementations log the ResultStatus of the service invocation.
